      "patchset_number": 9,
      "line": 31,
      "message": "To correctly connect to CertService API we need following on CMPv2Issuer side:\nURL - e.g. https://oom-cert-service:8443/v1/certificate/\nCA_NAME - e.g. RA\nReference to secret with keystore and truststore (e.g. certServiceClient-keystore.jks && truststore.jks)\nReference to secret with passwords to above files (e.g. secret && secret) - this is different than when we used CertService client as init container\n\nWithin CertService client we have also REQUEST_TIMEOUT but such is not mandatory.",
